            <p>
                Exclusive is a modern and user-friendly e-commerce platform developed using 
                ASP.NET Core MVC. This project is designed to provide a seamless online shopping 
                experience for users, allowing them to explore products, add items to their cart, 
                and place orders efficiently.
            </p>

            <p>
                The platform includes essential e-commerce functionalities such as user 
                authentication (registration and login), product browsing, shopping cart 
                management, secure checkout process, and order tracking system. It aims to 
                simulate real-world online shopping platforms like Flipkart and Amazon.
            </p>

            <p>
                Exclusive supports multiple product categories such as electronics, gaming 
                accessories, and gadgets. The system is designed with scalability in mind, 
                making it easy to extend features like payment gateway integration, admin 
                dashboard, and advanced filtering in the future.
            </p>

            <p>
                This project demonstrates strong concepts of web development including 
                MVC architecture, database integration using Entity Framework Core, session 
                management, and responsive UI design using Bootstrap.
            </p>
